However, according to <a href='http&#58;//vdt.cs.wisc.edu/vdt_140_cache/PPDG-' target='_blank' rel='nofollow'>http&#58;//vdt.cs.wisc.edu/vdt_140_cache/PPDG-</a>
Cert-Scripts.pacman the scripts should be there, right? We are
running 0.5.1 on the node, with VDT version 1.4.0

